Ranger Help for: nature's protection
======================================

SYNTAX:      rprotect
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   7
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to call upon Gaia for a protective aura
that surrounds the Ranger and reduces incoming damage for a duration.
The strength and duration of the protection depend on the Ranger's
wisdom and guild level. This aura is a gift from Gaia and works in
any terrain, though it is strongest in the Ranger's primary terrain.
The protection fades over time and must be renewed.
